{
  "id": "adv_event_2203_01_02",
  "title": "秘めたる才能",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは、元々私の声質が\n面白いって感じていたんだって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san originally found\nmy voice interesting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.438685035699999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど～、だからサニピのアルバムに、雫ちゃんの\nメインボーカルの曲を入れたいって話になったんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. That's why it was suggested to include a main vocal song\nby Shizuku-chan in Sunny Peace's album.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.6333333333,
      "endTime": 17.491541798900002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "雫の歌声、確かに特徴があって気にはなってた\n天性の才能だと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku's singing voice does have unique characteristics that caught my attention.\nI think it's a natural talent.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.7,
      "endTime": 24.3140134811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　今までのサニピにない曲が生まれそう\n凄くいいと思う！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! It seems like a song that we haven't had in Sunny Peace\nso far is going to come out‚ I think it's really good!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5,
      "endTime": 30.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……問題はその先",
      "translations": {
        "en": "… The problem is what comes after that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4,
      "endTime": 32.4521088123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "お話には、作曲家さんと作詞家さんも同席してて……\nつい、私、熱くなって語っちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the discussion‚ there were also composers and lyricists present…\nI ended up getting carried away and passionately talking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6666666667,
      "endTime": 42.9634017439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "語る？　何を？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Talking? About what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2,
      "endTime": 45.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、雫ちゃんは、アイドルにとっても詳しいんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Shizuku-chan is very knowledgeable about idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8666666667,
      "endTime": 50.1894556682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "すみません……私、アイドルオタクなんです……\nトリエルも大好きでした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry… I'm an idol otaku…\nI used to love TRINITYAiLE…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.4,
      "endTime": 59.3414289475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "違った。今も、好き、です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I still do love now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5333333333,
      "endTime": 63.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ありがとう。なんだか、照れくさいけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ thank you. It's a bit shy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.3,
      "endTime": 67.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "その場にいたクリエイターさんは\n数々のアイドルに楽曲を提供している神クリエイター",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One of the creators who was there\nis a god-like creator who has provided music to numerous idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8,
      "endTime": 75.4387162859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "なのでつい……曲の良さについて\n気が付けば、機関銃のように、語っていた私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ without realizing it‚\nI started talking passionately about the quality of the song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6666666667,
      "endTime": 84.9305429799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "……自分のことじゃなくて\n曲のことをアピールしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You were promoting\nthe song instead of yourself?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1,
      "endTime": 89.23333333330001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "はい、神々に感謝の気持ちを伝えたくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I wanted to express my gratitude to the gods…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.3666666667,
      "endTime": 93.9453059833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、雫ちゃんらしいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha‚ that's so like you‚ Shizuku-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1333333333,
      "endTime": 96.9158276875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら、神々はとても気を良くして……\nノリノリで、私の曲を作ると約束してくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ the gods became very pleased…\nThey promised to create my song",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1,
      "endTime": 107.8478902274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "絶対、渾身の出来にするからって\nそして、ぜひ、シングルカットをと言われて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "with great enthusiasm and\nsaid they wanted it to be released as a single…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0666666667,
      "endTime": 115.6837795735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "凄いよ！　雫ちゃん、単独デビューだね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's amazing! Shizuku-chan‚ it's a solo debut for you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.8666666667,
      "endTime": 120.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "まだ、決まってない……\nさくらちゃん達にも、相談しないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not decided yet…\nI have to talk to Sakura-chan and the others…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5,
      "endTime": 126.17224952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "みんななら絶対に応援してくれるよ\n私もCD買っちゃう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone will definitely support you.\nI'll even buy the CD!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.3666666667,
      "endTime": 131.2990772365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私、なんか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But me? I feel like……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.6,
      "endTime": 135.0895692348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに謙遜することはないわ\n雫はとても魅力的なアイドルよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no need to be so modest.\nShizuku‚ you're a very charming idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3,
      "endTime": 140.46338091779998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "サニピの中だと、一歩後ろに下がっているように見える\nでも、凄く高いポテンシャルを秘めてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Among Sunny Peace‚ you seem to be taking a step back‚\nbut you have a great potential.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.6666666667,
      "endTime": 148.2942445119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "き、恐縮です……。でも、やっぱり私に\nソロデビューなんて無理、です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-thank you… But still‚ for me…\nI think a solo debut is impossible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.4666666667,
      "endTime": 157.53333333330002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……どうして、そんな風に思うの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Why do you think that way?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.7,
      "endTime": 160.23333333329998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルがソロで歌うのは凄いこと……\n特別な人だけが出来る……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a remarkable thing for an idol to sing solo…\nIt's something only special people can do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.4333333333,
      "endTime": 167.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "それこそ、麻奈さんや、瑠依さんのように……\n私には、無理です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like Manna-san and Rui-san…\nIt's impossible for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.3,
      "endTime": 175.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "待って、どうして自分から可能性を閉ざすの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ why do you close off your own possibilities like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.3333333333,
      "endTime": 178.9333332856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
